<!-- Title -->
Tennis Ball Collecting Robot
<!-- Content -->
<div class="main">
  <div class="title">Tennis Ball Collecting Mobile Robot</div>

  <div class="gallery">
    <div>
      <div class="heading">What did we build?</div>

      <p>
        We set out to design and construct an autonomous mobile robot which collects tennis balls inside a tennis court quadrant and deposits them in a
        cardboard box. The project was subject to time, cost and materials constraints, prompting us to make several difficult tradeoffs to ensure reliable
        operation during the final demonstration for the project unit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="primary-image-container">
      <img class="gallery-image image-landscape" src="./img/3-tennis-ball/Thumbnail.png" alt="Tennis ball" />
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="heading">Key Technical Skills</div>

      <ul>
        <li>Raspberry Pi programming</li>
        <li>STM32 microcontroller programming</li>
        <li>3D CAD - Solidworks</li>
        <li>Control systems</li>
        <li>Protoboarding</li>
        <li>Computer vision</li>
        <li>Machine learning</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

